version 2.0.3 (01/13/2010)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bugfix release clarifying what should be considered "streaming" data.

	* Don't consider being in transparent mode as necessarily being streaming
	  data
	

version 2.0.2 (01/12/2010)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version number update.

	* Synchronize version number of module with repo.
	

version 2.0.1 (01/12/2010)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Bugfix release targeting transparent mode.

	* Add memory constraint checks when in transparent mode
	* Use atomic memory allocation when in transparent mode


version 2.0.0 (01/07/2010)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is the initial release of the 2.0 driver series.
